Class HantoPieceDevelopment

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mygdx.hanto.implementation.core.HantoPieceDevelopment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HantoPiece

    public class HantoPieceDevelopment
extends java.lang.Object
implements HantoPiece
    This class is used to specifiy a piece of Delta Hanto and a hex on the board where the piece will be placed. This class is only used for testing purposes.
